text: @FedEx and @Safeway, you have made my day rather shitty. Just sayin’!  Get an actual email address not just some damn form for me to fill out. That way I can share the joy with everyone. You both suck!

@alandprice Alan - This is Teresa with FedEx Social Media. How may I help you? If you need assistance with a package, please DM your name, delivery address, tracking/phone numbers and an e-mail address. Thank you

@FedExHelp Thank you, it’s being handled I hope. I’m just a little frustrated right now. Your website says I can drop off a package at Safeway, but when I talked with someone at FedEx they said that I shouldn’t have done that. And @safeway in Arlington,  VA has really dropped the ball.
